---
/**
 * Testimonial - Social proof from real customer
 *
 * Single testimonial for focused impact.
 * Placed after Results to reinforce credibility.
 */
---

<section class="py-12 md:py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="reveal-on-scroll mx-auto max-w-2xl">
      <!-- Quote card -->
      <div class="relative rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-surface-raised p-6 md:p-8">
        <!-- Quote icon -->
        <div class="absolute -top-4 left-6 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand text-surface">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="currentColor"
            class="h-4 w-4"
          >
            <path d="M4.583 17.321C3.553 16.227 3 15 3 13.011c0-3.5 2.457-6.637 6.03-8.188l.893 1.378c-3.335 1.804-3.987 4.145-4.247 5.621.537-.278 1.24-.375 1.929-.311 1.804.167 3.226 1.648 3.226 3.489a3.5 3.5 0 01-3.5 3.5c-1.073 0-2.099-.49-2.748-1.179zm10 0C13.553 16.227 13 15 13 13.011c0-3.5 2.457-6.637 6.03-8.188l.893 1.378c-3.335 1.804-3.987 4.145-4.247 5.621.537-.278 1.24-.375 1.929-.311 1.804.167 3.226 1.648 3.226 3.489a3.5 3.5 0 01-3.5 3.5c-1.073 0-2.099-.49-2.748-1.179z" />
          </svg>
        </div>

        <!-- Quote text -->
        <blockquote class="text-lg leading-relaxed md:text-xl">
          Vi trengte en nettside som lastet raskt og så profesjonell ut. Nettup leverte på under to uker – og resultatet snakker for seg selv.
          <span class="text-brand">95 i ytelse og under ett sekund lastetid.</span>
          Endelig en leverandør som faktisk forstår hva som fungerer.
        </blockquote>

        <!-- Author -->
        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4">
          <!-- Avatar placeholder with initials -->
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand/10 text-brand font-semibold">
            SE
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Stein Eriksen</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">Daglig leder, iGive</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Optional: Link to full case study -->
      <p class="reveal-on-scroll reveal-delay-1 mt-6 text-center text-sm text-text-muted">
        <a href="/prosjekter" class="text-brand hover:text-brand-light">
          Se hele prosjektet
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
